casebody.data:
MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

91-2095. Hertz Corp. v. West Virginia Ins. Guar. Assn.

Franklin County, No. 91AP-67. This cause, here on appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County, was considered in the manner prescribed by law. Upon consideration of the joint application to dismiss,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective June 2, 1992.
